trigger.comments: The rate at which pages are [read from + written to disk] to resolve hard page faults. This counter is a primary indicator of the types of faults that cause system-wide delays. The count includes pages retrieved to satisfy page faults in the file system cache. These pages are ordinarily requested by applications.
